sql: SELECT c.cmi_cross_ref_id FROM Benefits_Overpayments AS c JOIN Council_Tax ON Council_Tax.council_tax_id = c.council_tax_id
SELECT AVG(s.electoral_register_id), s.cmi_cross_ref_id FROM Electoral_Register AS s WHERE s.electoral_register_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND  s.cmi_cross_ref_id >= 13 LIMIT 10

SELECT source_system_code FROM CMI_Cross_References JOIN Customer_Master_Index ON CMI_Cross_References.master_customer_id = Customer_Master_Index.master_customer_id JOIN Benefits_Overpayments ON CMI_Cross_References.cmi_cross_ref_id = Benefits_Overpayments.cmi_cross_ref_id WHERE CMI_Cross_References.cmi_cross_ref_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND Benefits_Overpayments.cmi_cross_ref_id < 58 LIMIT 7
SELECT MAX(cmi_cross_ref_id) AS max_cmi_cross_ref_id FROM Benefits_Overpayments WHERE cmi_cross_ref_id > 53

SELECT MAX(Rent_Arrears.council_tax_id), COUNT(DISTINCT source_system_code), Council_Tax.cmi_cross_ref_id FROM CMI_Cross_References JOIN Council_Tax JOIN Customer_Master_Index JOIN Rent_Arrears ON CMI_Cross_References.master_customer_id = Customer_Master_Index.master_customer_id AND Council_Tax.cmi_cross_ref_id = CMI_Cross_References.cmi_cross_ref_id AND Rent_Arrears.cmi_cross_ref_id = CMI_Cross_References.cmi_cross_ref_id WHERE  CMI_Cross_References.master_customer_id >= 17 AND council_tax_id >= (SELECT AVG(council_tax_id) FROM Parking_Fines AS x) GROUP BY Council_Tax.cmi_cross_ref_id ORDER BY Council_Tax.cmi_cross_ref_id ASC

SELECT Council_Tax.cmi_cross_ref_id FROM Council_Tax JOIN CMI_Cross_References ON Council_Tax.cmi_cross_ref_id = CMI_Cross_References.cmi_cross_ref_id WHERE CMI_Cross_References.master_customer_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR cmi_cross_ref_id IN (SELECT cmi_cross_ref_id FROM Rent_Arrears)
SELECT business_rates_id, cmi_cross_ref_id FROM Business_Rates WHERE business_rates_id = 51 LIMIT 9
SELECT cmi_cross_ref_id, council_tax_id FROM Benefits_Overpayments WHERE  cmi_cross_ref_id = 53

SELECT T1.council_tax_id, T4.source_system_code FROM Council_Tax T1 JOIN CMI_Cross_References T4 ON T1.cmi_cross_ref_id = T4.cmi_cross_ref_id JOIN Customer_Master_Index T3 ON T4.master_customer_id = T3.master_customer_id JOIN Electoral_Register T2 ON T4.cmi_cross_ref_id = T2.cmi_cross_ref_id WHERE T3.master_customer_id < 50 LIMIT 1

SELECT source_system_code FROM CMI_Cross_References JOIN Benefits_Overpayments ON Benefits_Overpayments.cmi_cross_ref_id = CMI_Cross_References.cmi_cross_ref_id WHERE council_tax_id = (SELECT MIN(council_tax_id) FROM Rent_Arrears) GROUP BY source_system_code LIMIT 9

SELECT Benefits_Overpayments.cmi_cross_ref_id FROM CMI_Cross_References JOIN Benefits_Overpayments ON Benefits_Overpayments.cmi_cross_ref_id = CMI_Cross_References.cmi_cross_ref_id JOIN Electoral_Register ON CMI_Cross_References.cmi_cross_ref_id = Electoral_Register.cmi_cross_ref_id WHERE Benefits_Overpayments.council_tax_id <= 73 ORDER BY Benefits_Overpayments.cmi_cross_ref_id ASC
SELECT AVG(m.council_tax_id) AS avg_council_tax_id, m.cmi_cross_ref_id FROM Rent_Arrears AS m WHERE m.cmi_cross_ref_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR m.cmi_cross_ref_id >= 39 GROUP BY m.cmi_cross_ref_id

SELECT source_system_code FROM Council_Tax JOIN CMI_Cross_References ON Council_Tax.cmi_cross_ref_id = CMI_Cross_References.cmi_cross_ref_id JOIN Benefits_Overpayments ON Benefits_Overpayments.cmi_cross_ref_id = CMI_Cross_References.cmi_cross_ref_id JOIN Rent_Arrears ON Rent_Arrears.cmi_cross_ref_id = CMI_Cross_References.cmi_cross_ref_id;
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT x.cmi_details), x.cmi_details FROM Customer_Master_Index AS x JOIN CMI_Cross_References AS y ON x.master_customer_id = y.master_customer_id ORDER BY x.cmi_details DESC;

SELECT source_system_code, Rent_Arrears.cmi_cross_ref_id FROM CMI_Cross_References JOIN Benefits_Overpayments JOIN Rent_Arrears ON Benefits_Overpayments.cmi_cross_ref_id = CMI_Cross_References.cmi_cross_ref_id AND Rent_Arrears.cmi_cross_ref_id = CMI_Cross_References.cmi_cross_ref_id WHERE  Benefits_Overpayments.cmi_cross_ref_id <= 91 GROUP BY Rent_Arrears.cmi_cross_ref_id, source_system_code LIMIT 5;
SELECT AVG(Rent_Arrears.cmi_cross_ref_id), COUNT(DISTINCT Rent_Arrears.cmi_cross_ref_id) FROM Rent_Arrears WHERE Rent_Arrears.cmi_cross_ref_id >= 25

SELECT e.master_customer_id, e.cmi_details FROM Customer_Master_Index AS e WHERE e.master_customer_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR e.master_customer_id <= 66 GROUP BY e.master_customer_id, e.cmi_details LIMIT 3

SELECT COUNT(electoral_register_id), COUNT(DISTINCT electoral_register_id), cmi_cross_ref_id FROM Electoral_Register WHERE electoral_register_id <= 95 AND electoral_register_id <= (SELECT MIN(electoral_register_id) FROM Electoral_Register WHERE electoral_register_id <= 2 LIMIT 1) AND cmi_cross_ref_id < 8 GROUP BY cmi_cross_ref_id ORDER BY cmi_cross_ref_id DESC

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT T2.council_tax_id), T1.cmi_cross_ref_id FROM CMI_Cross_References AS T1 INNER JOIN Benefits_Overpayments AS T2 ON T1.cmi_cross_ref_id = T2.cmi_cross_ref_id WHERE T2.council_tax_id <= 44 GROUP BY T1.cmi_cross_ref_id HAVING SUM(T2.cmi_cross_ref_id) >= 34 ORDER BY T1.cmi_cross_ref_id ASC LIMIT 5

SELECT Benefits_Overpayments.cmi_cross_ref_id, source_system_code FROM CMI_Cross_References JOIN Benefits_Overpayments ON Benefits_Overpayments.cmi_cross_ref_id = CMI_Cross_References.cmi_cross_ref_id WHERE master_customer_id = 88 AND EXISTS (SELECT * FROM Rent_Arrears AS x WHERE x.cmi_cross_ref_id >= 50 AND CMI_Cross_References.cmi_cross_ref_id = x.cmi_cross_ref_id) GROUP BY Benefits_Overpayments.cmi_cross_ref_id, source_system_code
SELECT cmi_cross_ref_id FROM Electoral_Register WHERE EXISTS (SELECT * FROM CMI_Cross_References AS w WHERE Electoral_Register.cmi_cross_ref_id = w.cmi_cross_ref_id)
SELECT T1.council_tax_id, T2.source_system_code FROM Benefits_Overpayments AS T1 JOIN CMI_Cross_References AS T2 ON T1.cmi_cross_ref_id = T2.cmi_cross_ref_id WHERE T2.cmi_cross_ref_id > 69
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT master_customer_id) FROM Customer_Master_Index WHERE master_customer_id != 68 LIMIT 1;

SELECT CMI_Cross_References.cmi_cross_ref_id, source_system_code FROM CMI_Cross_References JOIN Electoral_Register ON CMI_Cross_References.cmi_cross_ref_id = Electoral_Register.cmi_cross_ref_id WHERE CMI_Cross_References.master_customer_id < 29;

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT CMI_Cross_References.cmi_cross_ref_id), cmi_details FROM CMI_Cross_References JOIN Customer_Master_Index ON CMI_Cross_References.master_customer_id = Customer_Master_Index.master_customer_id JOIN Council_Tax ON Council_Tax.cmi_cross_ref_id = CMI_Cross_References.cmi_cross_ref_id WHERE Council_Tax.cmi_cross_ref_id <= 63 OR EXISTS (SELECT * FROM CMI_Cross_References WHERE Council_Tax.council_tax_id = cmi_cross_ref_id) GROUP BY cmi_details

SELECT COUNT(council_tax_id), source_system_code FROM CMI_Cross_References JOIN Electoral_Register JOIN Rent_Arrears ON CMI_Cross_References.cmi_cross_ref_id = Electoral_Register.cmi_cross_ref_id AND Rent_Arrears.cmi_cross_ref_id = CMI_Cross_References.cmi_cross_ref_id WHERE EXISTS (SELECT * FROM CMI_Cross_References WHERE CMI_Cross_References.cmi_cross_ref_id = Rent_Arrears.cmi_cross_ref_id LIMIT 8)

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT CMI_Cross_References.master_customer_id), COUNT(DISTINCT cmi_cross_ref_id), source_system_code FROM CMI_Cross_References JOIN Customer_Master_Index ON CMI_Cross_References.master_customer_id = Customer_Master_Index.master_customer_id WHERE  cmi_cross_ref_id <= 11
